n> is his most well-known and </span><em>Metal Machine Music</em><span> wil=
l always be one of those records people will swear up and down is a minimal=
ist masterpiece and if you don&#8217;t get that then you don&#8217;t unders=
tand music, but </span><em>New York</em><span> is his most American. The na=
me might make you think otherwise, but when I put it on for the first time =
this season, the first lyrics on the opening track, &#8220;Romeo Had Juliet=
te,&#8221; grabbed me:</span></p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(=
